        "east-orange": "East Orange properties fall under Essex County jurisdiction, meaning the Essex County Surrogate's Court in Newark is the venue where an executor must qualify before any inherited home can be sold or transferred. Given how frequently multi-family properties change hands in East Orange through estates, the Surrogate's office here sees a steady volume of filings, so moving early in the process helps avoid backlogs.",
