        "hackensack": "Hackensack is the seat of Bergen County, and foreclosure cases here are heard in the Bergen County Superior Court, which is located right in town — making it one of the more accessible courthouses in the state for homeowners wanting to monitor their own case. Bergen County's Chancery Division has historically managed a steady foreclosure docket, and the state's mandatory mediation program applies to owner-occupied homes here just as it does statewide.",
