        "burbank": "Burbank is located in Los Angeles County, and probate cases for inherited homes here are handled by the LA Superior Court — a system that, despite its size, routinely experiences scheduling gaps that can extend a straightforward probate past the 12-month mark. Burbank's media-industry-driven real estate market keeps home values well above the $184,500 affidavit threshold, so formal probate is almost always required, and families are often surprised by how long they're paying property taxes and insurance on a home they can't yet sell.",
